%% REFERENCES
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

\references{
Adams, R. J., & Wu, M. L. (2007). The mixed-coefficients multinomial logit model.
